{"type": "article", "id": 19876, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-29T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061456476eEVyR3G7cCLsKHU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这两盒清新的巧克力是寒冷冬日里的一份温暖的礼物。粉色和蓝色分别代表薄荷和太妃糖口味，而背景用了圆点排列出两种不同形式的图案，有点像雨点或雪花。盒子中间空出了白色的六角形做标签，上面用不同的黑色字体书写了名字，显得活泼可爱。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615023808P6OoredbDp4yZk.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"883\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150239c6GsV0dD2iph3uSY.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}